'''天主教瓦里教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Huariensis}}；{{lang-es|Diócesis de Huarí}}）是[[秘魯|秘魯]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教特魯希略總教區|特魯希略總教區]]。自治監督區於1958年5月15日設立，2008年4月2日升為教區。<ref>{{cite web |title=HUARIENSIS* |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/benedict-xvi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_ben-xvi_apc_20080402_huariensis.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2019-12-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216063411/https://w2.vatican.va/content/benedict-xvi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_ben-xvi_apc_20080402_huariensis.html |archivedate=2019-12-16 |language=la |date=2008-04-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

教區位於[[安卡什大區|安卡什大區]]東南部，2004年時有教友296,500人（佔轄區總人口96.9%）、二十個堂區和四十六名司鐸。現任教區主教為{{link-it|毅夫·巴爾迪-加布里|Ivo Baldi Gaburri}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 02.04.2008 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2008/04/02/0220/00505.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-12-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216062439/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2008/04/02/0220/00505.html |archivedate=2019-12-16 |language=it |date=2008-04-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-de|喬治·巴爾貝塔|Giorgio Barbetta}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 12.12.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/12/12/191212e.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-12-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191215093308/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/12/12/191212e.html |archivedate=2019-12-15 |language=en |date=2019-12-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休監督為{{link-de|丹泰·弗拉斯內利-塔爾泰爾|Dante Frasnelli Tarter}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 13.06.2001 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2001/06/13/0346/01004.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-12-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216062950/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2001/06/13/0346/01004.html |archivedate=2019-12-16 |language=it |date=2001-06-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

